  "category": "Input",
  "description": "Detect when Mouse and Keyboard keys were just pressed, and not held down.\nUseful for when you want Mouse/Keyboard events to be detected when the key/button is first pressed and not held down.\n\nTo use, add the appropriate Mouse / Keyboard conditions from the extension to the event conditions.\n\nFor example, to make sure a button is only triggered when it is clicked and not when the mouse button is held down and dragged over it, create the following event:\n\n    Conditions:\n    - Mouse Button Left 'OnClick' Detected\n    - The cursor/touch is on 'Button'\n    \n    Events:\n    - Trigger any relevant button events",
